                <note rend="inline" type="source">761.93/159: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Crane</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1920-11-16T18:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 16, 1920—6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>335. Your 374, November 13, 1 a.m., and 375 of November 13, 9 p.m.</p>
                <p>You may join your colleagues in communicating note to Chinese Government.<note
                        n="31" xml:id="d823fn31">The note was communicated under date of Nov.
                        18.</note>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Colby</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
